{"tid":1217893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本來以為單野只有美國同台灣撐, 點撚知連日本議員都撐埋","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T14:49:40.000Z","uid":31637,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6bff19ce85f3c1436fda998082b034f4b9587bf","tid":1217893,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:45.000Z","msg":"有日本民間組織發起聯署，要求外務大臣河野太郎向香港特首林鄭月娥表明反對修訂《逃犯條例》，以及反對「向非暴力遊行示威進行暴力鎮壓」。<br />\n<br />\n聯署由日本 Youth Democracy Promotion Agency（YDPA）代表理事仁木崇嗣在 <a href=\"http://change.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAja0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=f73cb24d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">change.org</a> 發起，頁面約在香港時間下午 4 點創立，截至香港時間 19 時 45 分，署名人數為 105 人。此外，來自東京、大阪、靜岡、福岡、北海道、千葉、山口縣、愛知縣、岐阜縣等各級議會議員均留名表達支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E7%99%BC%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E5%A4%96%E7%9B%B8%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%8D%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B-%E5%85%A8%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%BE-40-%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81/?fbclid=IwAR22M2SoBQqELI89iGEGdTcyY4l40eP1NmWB3tpYvFDI2wAvkJdgDoq-TAU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259B%25B8%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%258F%258D%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2580%25BE-40-%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR22M2SoBQqELI89iGEGdTcyY4l40eP1NmWB3tpYvFDI2wAvkJdgDoq-TAU&d=ZtOroIbK3MFZ3s7JZysAja0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=1c461824\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%259